  "text": "The above assumption states that the cost of taking care is less than the decrease in the total litigation cost. This assumption implies that if the injurer knows the victim is going to sue when infringement occurs, he will take care. [CITATION_1] In section 6, we extend the model to incorporate variable cost of care. We also impose the following assumptions on the cost and value distributions.",
